____ is not an empty strong emphasis

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1 +1 @@
-____ is not an empty strong emphasis
+\_\_\_\_ is not an empty strong emphasis
```

# Output

```md
\_\_\_\_ is not an empty strong emphasis
```
